title: Rwanda women's national under-20 football team
text:
The Rwanda women's national under-20 football team represents Rwanda in international youth women's football competitions.
The team competed at the <a href="2022%20African%20U-20%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup%20Qualifying%20Tournament">2022 African U-20 Women's World Cup Qualifying Tournament</a> without qualifying for the <a href="2022%20FIFA%20U-20%20Women%27s%20World%20Cup">2022 FIFA U-20 Women's World Cup</a>.
